{"tid":1745670,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲另一半係咁","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:28:40.000Z","uid":13866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf864e99f1b0eb38feddb53147339880430a3f56","tid":1745670,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊個時糖痴豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你亦付出好多時間心機比對方<br />\n你好愛佢<br />\n佢都鍾意你<br />\n但佢話同你一齊唔會有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你忍唔住咁嘅關係想分手<br />\n佢就話好唔捨得 唔想你走<br />\n到底依種人諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f764e10b3bce3dbc56948ef95be4d029ce6083ec","tid":1745670,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"即係曬大家時間"},{"pid":"d3f47fe2bdac66edebb6545b6586cbc3a0c9bd4f","tid":1745670,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f764e10b3bce3dbc56948ef95be4d029ce6083ec","tid":1745670,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"即係曬大家時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"真係好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話因爲我地性格諗法唔同所以先咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但到我話分手佢又唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我又係廢嘅 其實唔想分所以一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beff6272dbbd0581f7c0284f1a45e8326878eef6","tid":1745670,"uid":158998,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"因為唔想自己一個<br />\n<br />\n平時相處無野果陣好地地好happy<br />\n但你做錯野時會即刻好撚憎你好想分手<br />\n但知你真係走時 驚覺又得番自己一個<br />\n就想你陪佢<br />\n即係好怕寂莫<br />\n你都識講你愛佢 佢只係鐘意你<br />\n所以佢係咁"},{"pid":"663e6431d8